to make his deadline.

317
00:19:09,798 --> 00:19:12,917
Is that so?

318
00:19:12,968 --> 00:19:15,303
I'll tell you what.
I'll make it simple for you.

319
00:19:15,337 --> 00:19:18,589
You give me the men
you made arrangements for today,

320
00:19:18,641 --> 00:19:22,010
and I'll give you Bohannon.

321
00:19:22,044 --> 00:19:23,928
