335
00:19:58,639 --> 00:20:00,273
Eva, I know
you're worth something.

336
00:20:00,307 --> 00:20:03,142
But I can't afford trouble
with your Mr. Ferguson.

337
00:20:03,193 --> 00:20:05,395
