to do with him.

338
00:20:05,429 --> 00:20:07,830
It's got everything
to do with him.

339
00:20:07,865 --> 00:20:10,400
He's out there right now.
He's angry, he's drunk.

340
00:20:10,434 --> 00:20:12,035
