368
00:21:55,339 --> 00:21:56,839
[Bell clangs]

369
00:22:01,345 --> 00:22:05,431
[Train conductor shouts
in distance]

370
00:22:05,482 --> 00:22:07,150
Hello.

371
00:22:07,184 --> 00:22:10,987
I need you to send a wire
to the Boston police department.

372
00:22:11,021 --> 00:22:13,523
Suspect by the name
of Sean McGinnes.

373
00:22:13,557 --> 00:22:16,109
S-E-A-N

374
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:19,746
M-C-G-I-N-N-E-S.

375
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:21,831
And have 'em get back to me
as soon as possible.

376
00:22:21,865 --> 00:22:25,401
Yes, sir.

377
00:22:28,205 --> 00:22:29,455
Thank you.

378
00:22:29,506 --> 00:22:32,408
Eva.

379
00:22:33,794 --> 00:22:35,094
I was worried about you
and the baby

380
00:22:35,129 --> 00:22:38,681
when I got word of the cholera.

381
00:22:41,351 --> 00:22:44,720
Oh, God.

382
00:22:44,754 --> 00:22:46,889
