- [Groans]

455
00:28:01,843 --> 00:28:04,191
Oh, brother, turn your head.
Something died in your mouth.

456
00:28:04,311 --> 00:28:05,912
Get up.
Now get up.

457
00:28:05,947 --> 00:28:06,436
- Get your pants on.
- What's the matter?

458
00:28:06,563 --> 00:28:08,230
- We gotta go.
- Something burning?

459
00:28:08,264 --> 00:28:10,099
We gotta go to New York,
get on the first train out.

460
00:28:10,133 --> 00:28:11,533
Get away from here.

461
00:28:11,568 --> 00:28:12,985
We going to New York.
Get your pants on.

462
00:28:13,036 --> 00:28:15,537
We ain't going
to no damn New York.

463
00:28:15,572 --> 00:28:16,956
- We got to.
- What?

464
00:28:16,990 --> 00:28:18,374
My baby girl there.
We gotta find her.

465
00:28:18,408 --> 00:28:19,992
You ain't getting
that baby back.

466
00:28:20,043 --> 00:28:21,877
- We can find her.
- What? We can't find her.

467
00:28:21,911 --> 00:28:23,746
- I need you.
- Look, your baby gone.

468
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:25,547
You hear me?

469
00:28:25,582 --> 00:28:29,335
You listen.
She gone.

470
00:28:29,386 --> 00:28:32,304
And you ain't getting her back.

471
00:28:32,339 --> 00:28:33,806
Hmm?

472
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:37,142
Now you think on--
you think on this now.

473
00:28:37,177 --> 00:28:39,762
Done been through too much.

474
00:28:39,796 --> 00:28:42,147
