I miss my baby girl.

483
00:29:10,993 --> 00:29:13,128
I miss my baby girl.

484
00:29:15,098 --> 00:29:18,133
Brother,

485
00:29:18,167 --> 00:29:20,302
she gone.

486
00:29:27,394 --> 00:29:29,361
[Man coughing]

