00:29:41,291 --> 00:29:43,358
[Man coughs]

489
00:29:45,628 --> 00:29:47,079
[Man snoring]

490
00:29:51,367 --> 00:29:54,870
- How you doing, Dutch?
- Awful, Mr. Bohannon.

491
00:29:57,590 --> 00:29:59,141
