520
00:31:06,376 --> 00:31:08,877
Yah! Yah! Yah! Yah!

521
00:31:08,912 --> 00:31:10,162
Wait, hold, hold.

522
00:31:10,213 --> 00:31:11,997
Damn it, boy.

523
00:31:12,048 --> 00:31:13,799
